title: Homelement.com Introduces the Duck Dynasty Licensed Sofa Sets and Recliners from Catnapper and Jackson Furniture
text:
Homelement.com is pleased to showcase the Duck Dynasty licensed sofa sets and recliners from Catnapper and Jackson Furniture.
East Brunswick, NJ (PRWEB) October 09, 2015
Homelement.com is pleased to introduce the Duck Dynasty licensed sofa sets and recliners from Catnapper and Jackson Furniture. These unique collections feature sofa sets, sectionals and recliners in multiple fabric patterns as well as storage ottomans. The well known features such as lay flat reclining and power options are also available on certain items. Browse through their many collections to find the set that works best for your home here .
The Duck Dynasty Appalachian Collection offers a casual comfort design with decorative toss pillows, extra wide seating and tall back, super soft heavy weight fabric, and available power reclining. This collection offers a lay flat recliner sofa or a Queen sleeper sofa, a console love seat and Sectional option. Lay flat matching recliner is also available to add to this unique set.
Catnapper also offers the Duck Dynasty Chimney Rock Collection of recliners with 4 fabric options and two other Camo styled recliners from classic Catnapper designs. The Chimney Rock Collection offers a transitional design with incredible comfort, extra wide automotive seating, and an extra tall rounded back.
Jackson Furniture also offers a few different collections for the Duck Dynasty line. The Duck Dynasty Huntley Collection features casual contemporary design, pillow top seat, padded arms and comfort coil seating with comfort-gel with a sofa and love seat available.
Lastly, the Duck Dynasty Homestead Collection features extra deep T-cushioned design, reversible seat cushions, attached bordered backs, individual hand driven brass nails, versatile toss pillows. Also available, a uniquely designed correlate rocker recliner and comfort coil seating with comfort-gel.
About Homelement
Homelement.com is a leading retail supplier of stylish and elegant home furnishings with more than a dozen years of industry experience. Homelement offers the complete selection of Catnapper and Jackson furniture at great prices including Catnapper recliners, power lift chairs, and Jackson reclining sofa sets.
